        {
            "title": "涉聖誕前夕襲擊女友致不治 45歲菲籍男傭工否認謀殺開審",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"菲籍被告VALENCIA Bernie Macatangay否認謀殺女友QUIABANG Ivy Villaluz受審。資料圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a82d25f4e3d070bb8c92ef23cfd11e0e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250328/_2025032814140735696.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">菲籍被告VALENCIA Bernie Macatangay否認謀殺女友QUIABANG Ivy Villaluz受審。資料圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>男菲籍傭工涉兩年前的聖誕前夕，在灣仔板間房內毆打40歲同居女友，致女方失禁及身上多處瘀傷，拖延到翌日才由鄰居揭發報警，女方終因顱內出血死亡。涉案45歲男子今早在高等法院否認謀殺罪開審。控方開案陳詞指，被告向救護員聲稱，死者在廁所內滑倒，惟被告沒有透露曾攻擊死者頭部。\n\n</p>\n<p>45歲菲律賓籍被告VALENCIA Bernie Macatangay，案發時為外籍傭工，被控一項謀殺罪。控罪指他於2022年1月2日謀殺QUIABANG Ivy Villaluz。案發時，40歲菲律賓籍死者同為外籍傭工，與被告為情侶關係。\n\n</p>\n<p>開案陳詞指，死者QUIABANG Ivy於2021年12月22日與男友、即被告VALENCIA Bernie Macatangay 一同參加聖誕派對後，返回位於灣仔的住所。2人其後發生爭吵，被告擊打死者的頭部，致其臉部及四肢出現瘀青，傷勢令她不能坐直，躺下時更失禁。控方指，被告應意識到死者需要接受緊急治療，卻無召喚警方或救護車。至翌日（23日）晚上，被告才要求鄰居探望住所內的死者。鄰居發現死者傷勢嚴重，立即報警求助。被告在救護員到達後，告知他們死者在廁所內滑倒。惟被告不曾表示，曾攻擊過死者的頭部。死者當晚送院，在2022年1月2日因顱內出血及腦損傷死亡。案件周一續審。\n\n</p>\n<p>案件編號：HCCC217/2024<br/>\n法庭記者：黃巧兒\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2060753/即時-港聞-涉聖誕前夕襲擊女友致不治-45歲菲籍男傭工否認謀殺開審",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-28 14:26:13",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "山東男30萬購豐田新車 中控台驚現白色人體蛋白質",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"豐田新車中控台驚現白色人體蛋白質。生活幫\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/bc5148b9dfe4b3badef4adba471b753c/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250328/_2025032814124335796.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">豐田新車中控台驚現白色人體蛋白質。生活幫</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>生活幫3月27日報道，近日，山東濟南天橋區，蘇先生花30多萬元人民幣在廣汽豐田濟南中升匡山店新買了一輛SIENNA汽車，提車後回家發現中控台有一處白色污漬，經檢測為人體蛋白質，想要4S店給出解釋。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"購車人蘇先生。生活幫\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e7ff4b6e96017ced15c5b0eb46a9948e/2025-03/951195e334774aec4da85a018430c3d.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        購車人蘇先生。生活幫\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"豐田新車中控台驚現白色人體蛋白質。生活幫\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/08471ee10bb8bc7261b83a2584cbfa52/2025-03/fa6d5141961220c3385f5268294beb6.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        豐田新車中控台驚現白色人體蛋白質。生活幫\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"購車門店。生活幫\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/345a5292b9b32b77a22e2de630190a88/2025-03/753f8bbca71a715befa1c11af67e409.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        購車門店。生活幫\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>面對採訪，4S店工作人員沒有正面回應，僅表示可以送幾次車輛保養。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2060752/即時-中國-山東男30萬購豐田新車-中控台驚現白色人體蛋白質",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-28 14:21:17",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "歐聯｜皇馬4子被歐洲足協調查面臨停賽 8強對手阿仙奴隨時漁人得利",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"皇馬4子被歐洲足協調查面臨停賽，歐聯8強對手阿仙奴隨時漁人得利。getty images\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/cc484fec959721c1691fdda5aa8d18bd/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250328/_2025032813362842384.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">皇馬4子被歐洲足協調查面臨停賽，歐聯8強對手阿仙奴隨時漁人得利。getty images</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>正所謂鷸蚌相爭，漁人得利，阿仙奴好有機會做漁人，因為歐洲足協周四官方宣布，就歐聯16強次回合皇家馬德里作客馬德里體育會，賽後有皇馬球員涉嫌向主場球迷做出挑釁行為，正式調查皇馬前鋒雲尼斯奧斯祖利亞(Vinicius Junior)、基利安麥巴比(Kylian Mbappe)、中場丹尼施巴路斯(Dani Ceballos)和中堅魯迪格(Antonio Rudiger)，4人有機會面對停賽處罰，隨時要缺席歐聯8強首回合作客阿仙奴，甚至兩回合都沒份上場。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"丹尼施巴路斯被指做不文動作。getty images\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c2ae5e76a99363aded6f78ea812de0d0/2025-03/GettyImages-2198504540.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        丹尼施巴路斯被指做不文動作。getty images\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"魯迪格向球迷做割頸動作。getty images\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4e96e4e90ebeb3b029a6fd320df55a6b/2025-03/GettyImages-2204933518.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        魯迪格向球迷做割頸動作。getty images\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"雲尼斯奧斯被指向球迷做開槍動作。getty images\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/33748763af3e209123b168170bdec448/2025-03/GettyImages-2206956493.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        雲尼斯奧斯被指向球迷做開槍動作。getty images\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"基利安麥巴比被指向球迷抓下體。getty images\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/339cc8f021e4620fef86b30830838b8d/2025-03/GettyImages-2206956695.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        基利安麥巴比被指向球迷抓下體。getty images\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"雲尼斯奧斯被指向球迷做射槍手勢。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f6c9f7cc6574510b15d5226fea30665a/2025-03/2025-03-09T155627Z_710029088_UP1EL3918A1VQ_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-SPAIN-RMA-RAY-REPORT_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        雲尼斯奧斯被指向球迷做射槍手勢。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"雲尼斯奧斯被指向球迷做射槍手勢。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8cb18b78ca41bde2c56d6b5e8b2c0895/2025-02/7_26.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        雲尼斯奧斯被指向球迷做射槍手勢。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"皇馬射手基利安麥巴比被指向球迷做抓下體動作。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/326813dbd54524aff0c137666339609a/2025-03/2025-03-09T174158Z_789785452_UP1EL39181FUY_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-SPAIN-RMA-RAY-REPORT_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        皇馬射手基利安麥巴比被指向球迷做抓下體動作。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"皇馬射手基利安麥巴比(右)被指向球迷做抓下體動作。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a50e15e522a5d53da27b86445f51248e/2025-03/2025-03-09T160233Z_766996203_UP1EL3918K7WT_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-SPAIN-RMA-RAY-REPORT_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        皇馬射手基利安麥巴比(右)被指向球迷做抓下體動作。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>歐洲足協正式調查皇馬4子</h2>\n<p>歐聯16強次回合皇馬作客0:1負馬體會，兩回合賽和2:2，皇馬最終互射12碼淘汰馬體會打入8強，賽後有馬體會球迷向場內投擲水樽等雜物，而部份皇馬球員於離場時向馬體會球迷做出挑釁動作，其中雲尼斯奧斯被指在比賽期間和賽後，合共6次向主場球迷做出射槍動作，而基利安麥巴比被指在離場時向球迷用手抓下體，魯迪格則被拍下在互射12碼後向球迷做出割頸動作，丹尼施巴路斯亦被指向球迷做不文手勢。\n\n</p><h2>4人面臨歐聯8強對阿仙奴停賽</h2>\n<p>馬體會於賽後向歐洲足協投訴，並褫交4名涉事皇馬球員挑釁主場球迷的片段，而歐洲足協周四官方宣布立案調查4人，若最終被裁定罪成，4人勢遭到歐洲足協施以停賽處罰，而停賽期可以是1場或者更多。而皇馬下場歐洲賽是4月8日歐聯8強首回合作客阿仙奴，之後於4月16日的次回合主場再戰兵工廠；若4人最終被罰歐聯8強首回合、甚至兩回合停賽，阿仙奴便可漁人得利。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2060748/即時-體育-歐聯-皇馬4子被歐洲足協調查面臨停賽-8強對手阿仙奴隨時漁人得利",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-28 14:11:34",
